        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:33:5",
        "text": [
          " أَصْحَابُ الْكَبَائِرِ كُلِّهَا إِذَا أُقِيمَ عَلَيْهِمُ الْحُدُودُ مَرَّتَيْنِ قُتِلُوا فِي الثَّالِثَةِ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Muhammad, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Safwan, from Yunus, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan Al-Maazy<sup>asws</sup> (7<sup>th</sup> Imam<sup>asws</sup>) having said: ‘The commiters of the major sins, all of them, the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) would be established upon them twice. They would be killed during the third’."
          ]
        }
      }
